Class adress

java.lang.Object
adress
public class adress
extends java.lang.Object
This class stores and handles a canadian address containing street, street number, city province and postal code.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor Description
    adress()
    Default constructor initiates the object with an empty address.
